local lastX = 0 local stepIncrement = 1.0 / self.properties.gridSteps
function onValueChanged() local d = math.abs(lastX - self.values.x);
if d > 0.5 then d = math.abs(d - 1) end
if d < stepIncrement then return true end
lastX = math.floor((self.values.x / stepIncrement) + 0.5) * stepIncrement if math.abs(1 - lastX) < 0.01 then lastX = 0 end end
